'''Butcher of Renatasia''' was the title given to [[Vuffi Raa]] by the survivors of a [[Centrality/Legends|Centrality]]-[[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Battle of Renatasia|assault]] on [[Renatasia/Legends|Renatasia]] in the early years of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. They believed Raa provided information to the Imperials and their Centrality allies that led to the attack, though the true "Butcher" turned out to be an individual named [[Osuno Whett/Legends|Osuno Whett]]. The Renatasians referred to this event as [[Battle of Renatasia|''The Betrayal'']].

